Description:
    Generate scaffold from JSON Schema

Example:
    rails generate json_schema:scaffold Thing

    This will create:
        Controller: app/controllers/users_controller.rb
        Model:      app/models/user.rb
        Serializer: app/serializers/user_serializer.rb
        Factory:    spec/factories/users.rb
        Tests:      spec/controllers/users_controller_spec.rb
                    spec/models/user_spec.rb
                    spec/serializers/user_serializerspec.rb
                    spec/requests/users_spec.rb
